PPIP - Peter's CP/M PIP Clone/Variant

Copyright (c) Peter Eriksson <pen@lysator.liu.se>

At last - you have been waiting long for this valuable tool to be
available on Unix systems. And here it is. A clone of the CP/M
Peripheral Interchange Program - aka PIP - utility.


